{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"95mp2snular2q0j2irih6ht","title":"Vue","desc":"","updated":1687536937494,"created":1687536128513,"custom":{},"fname":"web-components.frameworks-integration.vue","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"adf57bc25976b7cb7b65c547edbbcead","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.frameworks-integration.vue","id":"95mp2snular2q0j2irih6ht","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.deployment.npm","alias":"Dropdown","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":75,"offset":238},"end":{"line":3,"column":117,"offset":280},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.deployment.npm"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"web-components.frameworks-integration.vue","id":"95mp2snular2q0j2irih6ht","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"web-components.frameworks-integration.angular","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":58,"offset":1794},"end":{"line":66,"column":107,"offset":1843},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web-components.frameworks-integration.angular"}},{"from":{"fname":"web-components.frameworks-integration","id":"hgfihscw1sv5ewje8sm80r9","vaultName":"docs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":3,"offset":195},"end":{"line":4,"column":48,"offset":240},"indent":[]},"value":"web-components.frameworks-integration.vue"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"hgfihscw1sv5ewje8sm80r9","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"vue\">Vue<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#vue\"></a></h1>\n<p>Vue es un framework de javascript más nuevo que Angular o React que recientemente ha ganado popularidad por su simpleza en su API y la facil curva de aprendizaje.</p>\n<p>En esta sección crearemos un proyecto con VueJS Cli y agregaremos nuestro <a href=\"/notes/pizkajsyb0lra3nyjuiueiq\">Dropdown</a> al proyecto.</p>\n<p>Usaremos la herramienta de Vue CLI para generar el proyecto. Nos proveera todas las herramientas necesarias para generar el buildeo y correr nuestra aplicación. </p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g @vue/cli\nvue create my-app\n</code></pre>\n<p>Este comando creara nuestro proyecto e instalara las dependencias. Procedemos a instalar nuestro componente</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> web-component-essentials --save\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ahora podemos importarlo en nuestro <code>main.js</code> de la aplicación de Vue.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Vue</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'vue'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token imports\"><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">App</span></span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./App.vue'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'web-component-essentials'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">Vue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">config</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">productionTip</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Vue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">render</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">h</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">h</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token maybe-class-name\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">$mount</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#app'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Para correr la aplicación corremos</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run serve\n</code></pre>\n<p>Esto iniciará nuestra aplicación en <code>localhost:8080</code>. Vamos a ver nuestro componente <code>HelloWorld.vue</code>. Vue organiza todo en un sólo archivo (los estilos, el template y el script).</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">//HelloWorld.vue\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>VueJS Application using Web Components<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>{{show ? 'open': 'closed'}}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>x-dropdown</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">:title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>myTitle<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">@show</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>log<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      Hello from Web Component in Vue\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>x-dropdown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n  <span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword module\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'HelloWorld'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token function-variable function\">data</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">myTitle</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'project-vue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">show</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">methods</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function-variable function\">log</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token console class-name\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">show</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">detail</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>En nuestra <code>template</code> tenemos una sintaxis similar a <a href=\"/notes/3m8fv43uyem4l9uc3y7780z\">Angular</a>, podemos ver la expresión <code>{{show ? 'open' : 'closed'}}</code>. En el Dropdown estamos usando la sintaxis de bindeo de Vue, esta sintaxis funciona bien con todos los HTML elements asi como tambien custom elements usando Web Components.</p>\n<p>Para bindear una propiedad en vue usamos el <code>:</code> en este caso <code>:title=\"myTitle\"</code>. Nuestro componente Vue tiene una propiedad <code>myTitle</code> que se le asigna al <code>title</code> del dropdown.\nPara escuchar eventos, usamos el <code>@</code>, en este caso escuchamos nuestro evento show con <code>@show=\"log\"</code>.</p>\n<p>En el <code>script</code> definimos la data y los metodos de nuestro componente que vamos a querer bindear en el template.</p>\n<p>Vue es una muy buena opción liviana para crear aplicaciones JS que funcionen bien con Web Components.</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/hgfihscw1sv5ewje8sm80r9\">Frameworks Integration</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1687553787663,"created":1687478467553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb6d2289d9babdad43709e4ff265bef2","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"https://webcomponent.dev/","alias":"Cory Rylan","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":94,"offset":117},"end":{"line":4,"column":134,"offset":157},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"https://webcomponent.dev/"}}],"anchors":{"web-components-docs":{"type":"header","text":"Web Components DOCS","value":"web-components-docs","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["zkfccjgcs7b7pqvirwby57p"],"parent":